Heat barbecue to medium-high heat. Mix meat, bread crumbs and 1/2 cup Cooking Creme; shape into 12 (1/2-inch-thick) patties. Grill 3 to 4 min. on each side or until done (160F). Place arugula on bottom halves of buns; top with burgers and remaining Cooking Creme. Cover with tops of buns. Garnish with tomatoes.